  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to collect the prevalence of geriatric syndrome, which is
      recognized by an internist, and to compare the data based on the comprehensive geriatric
      assessment by a geriatrician. The secondary outcome is to develop a practical collected form
      for the internist.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
